  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Improving operational efficiency for better service delivery</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Rushere Sacco intends to decrease poverty among the nearly 8 000 members. The Sacco has a good track record and reputation  confirmed by staff  members and stakeholders. The management is experienced and capable. The Sacco now has a new manager and recently elected a new Board  they are highly motivated and eager to do better and leverage on the achievement of the old administration. With the coming of the new law regulating Sacco  (Tier 4 Micro-finance and money lenders act) this has necessitated Rushere to reorganise and position themselves to embrace the new reality for better compliance and serve their members better. The areas that need to be strengthened include.
Design a Robust Performance management system  Launching mobile banking to support the digitization efforts to further enhance our financial inclusion strategy. Tailored Credit management training for Branch managers  credit Officers on client selection  loan appraisal and monitoring. Support customer engagement forums to solicit feedback from both customers and potential customers to create avenues for sustainable savings mobilization</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Project plan is to achieve the project goal in a period of not more than 2 years by focusing on building internal capacities and systems supported by both Agriterra and the Sacco. This will focus on the following areas.   Design a Robust Performance management system  Launching mobile banking to support the digitization efforts to further enhance our financial inclusion strategy.Tailored Credit management training for Branch managers  credit Officers on client selection  loan appraisal and monitoring. Support customer engagement forums to solicit feedback from both customers and potential customers to create avenues for sustainable savings mobilization.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The goals of the project are 
1. Create an effective HR management model to better manage staff performance  improve skills and retain good Talent. 
2. Improve credit Management and Keep Loan portfolio performance under a single digit. 
3. Improve customer satisfaction across all branches.</narrative>
  </description>
